### Login as admin
# @name login
POST http://localhost:7331/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login as regular user
POST http://localhost:7331/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "bob@example.com",
  "password": "pass456"
}

### Invalid credentials (→ 401)
POST http://localhost:7331/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "wrong"
}

### Get current user (replace TOKEN with value from login response)
GET http://localhost:7331/api/me
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### Access admin dashboard as alice (admin role → 200)
GET http://localhost:7331/api/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### Access admin dashboard without token (→ 401)
GET http://localhost:7331/api/admin/dashboard

### Health check
GET http://localhost:7331/health
